cutter <- worker()
new_user_word(cutter, segment_not)
[1] TRUE
stopWords <- readRDS("data/stopWords.rds")
tokenized.df <- news.df %>%
    mutate(timestamp=ymd(time)) %>%
    select(-time) %>%
    select(title, text, cat, timestamp, everything()) %>%
    mutate(word = purrr::map(text, function(x)segment(x, cutter)))
word.count <- tokenized.df %>%
    unnest(word) %>%
    count(word, sort=T) %>%
    filter(!(word %in% stopWords$word)) %>%
    filter(nchar(word) > 1) %>%
    filter(!str_detect(word, "[a-zA-Z0-9]+")) %>%
    filter(n > 3)
unnested.df <- tokenized.df %>%
    select(doc_id, text, word) %>%
    unnest(word) %>%
    filter(!(word %in% stopWords$word)) %>%
    filter(!str_detect(word, "[a-zA-Z0-9]+"))

word.count %>%
    count(n, sort=T) %>%

cat_word_count <- tokenized.df %>%
    unnest(word) %>%
    count(cat, word) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    filter(!str_detect(word, "[a-zA-Z0-9]+")) %>%
    filter(!(word %in% stopWords$word)) %>%
    filter(nchar(word)>1)
early_lat_ratio <- cat_word_count %>%
    filter(n>1) %>%
    spread(cat, n, fill = 0) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    mutate_if(is.numeric, funs((. + 1) / sum(. + 1))) %>%
    mutate(logratio = log2(early / lat)) %>%
    arrange(desc(logratio))
early_lat_ratio %>%
    group_by(logratio > 0) %>%
    top_n(20, abs(logratio)) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    mutate(word = reorder(word, logratio)) %>%
    ggplot(aes(word, logratio, fill = logratio < 0)) +
    geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
    coord_flip() +
    ylab("early / recent log ratio") +
    scale_fill_manual(name = "", labels = c("early", "recent"),
        values = c("tomato", "lightblue")) +
    theme(axis.text.y=element_text(colour="black", family="Heiti TC Light"))

frequency <- cat_word_count %>%
    filter(n>3) %>%
    group_by(cat) %>%
    mutate(proportion = n/sum(n)) %>%
    select(-n) %>%
    spread(cat, proportion) %>%
    na.omit()

3 bigram

# recombined.df <- tokenized.df %>%
#     select(doc_id, word) %>%
#     unnest(word) %>%
#     group_by(doc_id) %>%
#     summarize(string = paste0(word, collapse = ",")) %>%
#     ungroup()
# recombined.df %>% head() %>% View()
five.gram <- unnested.df %>%
    select(doc_id, word) %>%
    group_by(doc_id) %>%
    mutate(w2 = lead(word, 1)) %>%
    mutate(w3 = lead(word, 2)) %>%
    mutate(w4 = lead(word, 3)) %>%
    mutate(w5 = lead(word, 4)) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    filter(complete.cases(.)) %>%
    mutate(w12 = paste0(word, " ", w2)) %>%
    mutate(w13 = paste0(word, " ", w3)) %>%
    mutate(w14 = paste0(word, " ", w4)) %>%
    mutate(w15 = paste0(word, " ", w5))
bigrams <- five.gram %>%
    select(doc_id, w12, w13, w14, w15) %>%
    gather("pair", "bigram", 2:5) %>%
    select(doc_id, bigram) %>%
    separate(bigram, c("word1", "word2"), sep = " ")
bigrams %>% slice(1:20) %>% View()
bigrams.count <- bigrams %>%
    count(word1, word2, sort = T)
bigrams.count %>% slice(200:400) %>% View()
bigram_tf_idf <- bigrams %>%
    unite(bigram, word1, word2, sep = " ") %>%
    count(doc_id, bigram) %>%
    bind_tf_idf(bigram, doc_id, n) %>%
    arrange(desc(n))
bigram_tf_idf %>%
    arrange(desc(tf_idf)) %>%
    slice(1:100) %>% View()
bigrams.count %>%
    ggplot(aes(n)) +
    geom_histogram(bins = 100)  + 
    scale_y_log10() + 
    scale_x_log10()

bigrams.filtered <- bigrams.separated %>%
    filter(word1 != word2) %>%
    filter(!word1 %in% stopWords$word) %>%
    filter(!word2 %in% stopWords$word)
